"https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-asks-fan-what-are-you-doing-sitting-down-before-realising-theyre-in-a-wheelchair-3599101">最近在一场演出中公开失礼，她问为什么一位歌迷还坐在座位上，结果才意识到他们坐在轮椅上</a>。</p><p>在同一场演出中，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-and-madonna-duet-for-international-womens-day-its-been-a-long-time-coming-3598605">欢迎凯莉·米洛登上舞台，进行现场二重唱，庆祝国际妇女节</a>。两位流行偶像演唱了《Can&#39;t Get You Out Of My Head》以及格洛丽亚·盖诺的《I Will Survive》。</p><p>这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-reveals-first-words-she-spoke-after-waking-up-from-coma-3597327#:~:text=Madonna%20has%20revealed%20the%20first,in%20the%20hospital%20last%20year.&amp;text=The%20pop%20star%20faced%20a,being%20admitted%20to%20the%20ICU.">最近在舞台上讲述了去年她因严重细菌感染被送进重症监护室后的“濒临死亡的经历”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cardi-b-join-madonna-on-stage-for-los-angeles-stint-of-celebration-tour-3600137">《Watch Cardi B》与麦当娜一起登上洛杉矶“Celebration”巡演舞台的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
